lead_paragraph: Wales produced a stunning upset to reach the Euro 2016 semi-finals after Hal Robson-Kanu's superbly fashioned goal and Sam Vokes's late header secured a 3-1 comeback win over Belgium on Friday to set up a clash with Portugal.

headline.print_headline: Wales Down Belgium to Reach First Ever Semi-Final
headline.main: Wales Down Belgium to Reach First Ever Semi-Final
